==Additional note==
Of the other companions of Thorin Oakenshield in the quest of Erebor, ''Ori'', ''Nori'', and ''Dori'' were also of the House of Durin, but were more remote kinsman.  ''Bifur'', ''Bofur'', and ''Bombur'' were descended from Dwarves of Khazad-dûm but not of Durin's line.<ref name="Durin"/>
